  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>flexible strategy</strong> card game infused with <strong>Rogue-lite</strong> elements, where every adventure brims with unpredictability. Confronting randomized dungeons, unexpected events, and a multiverse setting, each choice you make will forge a completely unique gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Deck , Explore Endless Dungeons!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/fc8af0c6569b4387a87d16824b8885f0.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=81 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The '1+4' minimalist deck-building system : 1 core card + 4 support cards</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five elements : Water, Fire, Wood, Light, Dark – craft unpredictable builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse rune customization : unique abilities to elevate your combat experience<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/14da32f2450a39c8a6f4cf6860e20afe.poster.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/14da32f2450a39c8a6f4cf6860e20afe.webm?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/14da32f2450a39c8a6f4cf6860e20afe.mp4?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/5a8b73b5004126867ec884f52ecab78b.poster.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/5a8b73b5004126867ec884f52ecab78b.webm?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/5a8b73b5004126867ec884f52ecab78b.mp4?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/83bce9083eea02fc806e5080f46a063e.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=81 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 cards to strategize with,every battle presents a new deck-building challenge!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flexibly adapt your battle deck then immerse in strategic thrills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-run deck crafting & evolution: Even unwanted cards forge your path to power.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/2e140c5f949e0ce0449cc057188eeea7.poster.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/2e140c5f949e0ce0449cc057188eeea7.webm?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/2e140c5f949e0ce0449cc057188eeea7.mp4?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/2a66c3e9cb1b04c80771b444f395736a.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=81 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse dungeon modules: Every expedition ventures into the unknown.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fresh treasures & formidable foes await your discovery.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/d7f11556d65bbe00549eb3a8d4e6592d.poster.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/d7f11556d65bbe00549eb3a8d4e6592d.webm?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/d7f11556d65bbe00549eb3a8d4e6592d.mp4?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/293397205d9c2d0bffd8392887d3dfc1.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=81 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomized encounters await in your adventure,shape your destiny with every decision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recover, upgrade, or warp unpredictably,prove your mastery of strategy & serendipity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/159e8257cbdf724b8887103f3efcceeb.poster.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/159e8257cbdf724b8887103f3efcceeb.webm?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/159e8257cbdf724b8887103f3efcceeb.mp4?t=1773844626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/5c2e813d555160830bd09f299210506c.avif?t=1773844626\" width=800 height=81 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Salvage loots from failed runs,the meta progressions improve your power.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond a single dungeon.An intricate multiverse where infinite possibilities converge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras/894a1bcf49a4a8d5e3155c093977e311.avif?t=1773844626\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411020/extras_big/894a1bcf49a4a8d5e3155c093977e311.avif?t=1773844626 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>",
